✨ Save this Samyang’s @tangle_pasta Recipe - 15g Protein ✨ 

Samyang’s Tangle 
✨ 15 grams of protein 
‘✨ 7 grams of fiber
✨ Ready in 4 minutes
✨ 4 flavors: Creamy Mushroom, Garlic Oil, Bulgogi Alfredo, & Chunky Tomato

Ingredients 
* 1 pack of Tangled pasta noodles 
* 1 handful mushrooms, sliced 
* 1 ribeye steak
* Butter 
* Salt & pepper 

Instructions 
1. Add 1 1/3 cups of water to a saucepan & bring to a boil. 
2. Add Tangled pasta noodles & flakes. Cook for 4 minutes & stir frequently. 
3. Remove from heat, then add sauce & powder. Set some sauce & powder mixture aside for last step. 
4. Stir until the noodles have absorbed the sauce evenly. 
5. Meanwhile, butter up a pan & saute mushrooms for 5 minutes. 
6. In another pan, add butter & place steak. Cook for 3 minutes. Flip & cook for another 3 minutes. 
7. Assemble noodles, then add steak & mushroom. Top with remaining sauce mixture. 

#tangle #proteinpasta #letstangle #healthymeal

Plated, slurped, and Nonna-approved. 

1️⃣ Open your Creamy Mushroom pasta packet. 
2️⃣ Add noodles and flakes in 1 1/3 cups (10.5 oz) of boiling water for 4 minutes while stirring frequently. 
3️⃣ Remove from heat, add sauce & powder, and stir it up until the noodles have absorbed the sauce evenly.
4️⃣ Enjoy the chewy, saucy perfection.

And if you loved this flavor, wait till you try the rest: Garlic Oil, Bulgogi Alfredo, and Chunky Tomato.
